  "Verification mindset": "Mentalidad de verificación",
  "Used manual QA, unit/integration/playmode/editor tests, feature-specific test scenes, logs, assertions, profiler markers and bug reproduction workflows before handing changes to QA.": "Usé QA manual, tests unitarios/integración/playmode/editor, escenas de prueba específicas por feature, logs, asserts, profiler markers y workflows de reproducción antes de entregar cambios a QA.",
  "AI-assisted, not AI-dependent": "Asistido por IA, no dependiente de IA",
  "Uses ChatGPT, Copilot and Claude for codebase exploration, architecture review, porting support and edge-case checks, while keeping final decisions, verification and ownership human-led.": "Uso ChatGPT, Copilot y Claude para explorar codebases, revisar arquitectura, apoyar porting y comprobar edge cases, manteniendo las decisiones finales, la verificación y el ownership en manos humanas.",
  "Production C# systems, modular feature packages, profiling, QA verification, TeamCity builds, PR reviews and milestone stabilization under NDA-safe framing.": "Sistemas C# en producción, paquetes modulares de features, profiling, verificación QA, builds de TeamCity, PR reviews y estabilización de milestones con framing NDA-safe.",
  "Private C++ engine case study: SufferManager, Scene/GameObject/Component/System architecture, DisplayList/Command render flow, ResourceManager, ImGui editor, Lua, audio and Linux/AppImage packaging.": "Caso de estudio privado de motor C++: arquitectura SufferManager, Scene/GameObject/Component/System, flujo de render DisplayList/Command, ResourceManager, editor ImGui, Lua, audio y empaquetado Linux/AppImage.",
